data.description: Welcoming 55+ condo in Lakes of Environ! This two-bedroom, two-bathroom unit boasts an oversized enclosed balcony with pool and green space views. The main suite, generously sized, offers two walk-in closets and balcony access. The second bedroom is spacious with its own walk-in closet. Updated bathrooms add a modern touch. Enjoy the expansive and open living space, along with an eat-in kitchen featuring updated appliances and granite countertops. Lakes of Environ community features a cultural center/theater, fitness center, pickleball, tennis, and scenic bike/walking trails. Experience a vibrant 55+ lifestyle with these amenities!
